  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Given an array AAA of size NNN (1\u2264Ai\u22641001 \\le A_i \\le 1001\u2264Ai\u200b\u2264100), compute the number of triplets (i,j,k)(i, j, k)(i,j,k) satisfying the following conditions :\n\n\n1\u2264i,j,k\u2264N1 \\le i, j, k \\le N1\u2264i,j,k\u2264N\n\u2223Ai\u2212Ak\u2223=\u2223i\u2212j\u2223+\u2223j\u2212k\u2223|A_i - A_k| = |i - j| + |j - k|\u2223Ai\u200b\u2212Ak\u200b\u2223=\u2223i\u2212j\u2223+\u2223j\u2212k\u2223\n\nInput Format\n\nThe first line of input will contain a single integer TTT, denoting the number of test cases.\nEach test case consists of multiple lines of input.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains NNN - the size of the array AAA\nThe second line contains NNN integers - A1,A2,...ANA_1, A_2, ... A_NA1\u200b,A2\u200b,...AN\u200b.\n\n\n\n\nOutput Format\nFor each test case, output on a new line the number of valid triplets.",
    "constraints": [
      "1\u2264T\u22641041 \\le T \\le 10^41\u2264T\u2264104",
      "1\u2264N\u22642\u22c51051 \\le N \\le 2 \\cdot 10^51\u2264N\u22642\u22c5105",
      "1\u2264Ai\u22641001 \\le A_i \\le 1001\u2264Ai\u200b\u2264100",
      "The sum of NNN over all test cases does not exceed 2\u22c51052 \\cdot 10^52\u22c5105."
    ],
    "inputFormat": "",
    "outputFormat": "",
